The paper discusses deep autoregressive models for density estimation, which is a common topic in machine learning and falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also mentions using neural attention and meta learning techniques, which are commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) research. Additionally, the paper discusses image mirroring and handwriting tasks, which are related to natural language processing (cs.CL) and neural networks (cs.NE).
